      <div class="body conbody">
         <p class="p P">Insert clause 1352.271-83, <em class="ph i">Government Review, Comment, Acceptance and Approval,</em> in all solicitations and contracts for ship construction and ship repair.


</p>
      </div>
   </article><article class="topic concept nested2 Section" aria-labelledby="ariaid-title17" id="Section_1371_115_T48_50651481115"><h3 class="title topictitle3" id="ariaid-title17">
         <span class="ph autonumber">1371.115</span> Access to the vessel.</h3>
      <div class="body conbody">
